Trading,Economics,provides,its,users,with,access,to,economic,data,for,countries,including,historical,data,for,more,than,economic,indicators,exchange,rates,stock,market,indexes,government,bond,yields,and,commodity,prices,The,Trading,Economics,API,allows,users,to,make,calls,to,get,a,list,of,countries,get,a,list,of,indicators,get,a,matrix,of,countries,get,indicators,by,country,and,get,indicators,by,category,The,API,uses,REST,calls,and,returns,HTML,CSV,and,JSON